blumi — third-party notices
===========================

blumi bundles a curated snapshot of agent **skills** (SKILL.md files) from the
following third-party projects, embedded into the binary and written to
~/.blumi/skills on first run. Each is used under the MIT License; full license
texts are in crates/blumi-skills/bundled/licenses/.

- obra/superpowers            (prefix: sp-)     — MIT, Copyright (c) 2025 Jesse Vincent
  https://github.com/obra/superpowers
- leonxlnx/taste-skill        (prefix: taste-)  — MIT, Copyright (c) 2026 Leonxlnx
  https://github.com/leonxlnx/taste-skill
- jeffallan/claude-skills     (prefix: cs-)     — MIT, Copyright (c) 2025 Jeff Allan
  https://github.com/jeffallan/claude-skills

Skill folders are namespaced by the prefixes above to avoid collisions. To
refresh the vendored snapshot, run scripts/vendor-skills.sh.

The default MCP server set and catalog reference the Model Context Protocol
reference servers (modelcontextprotocol/servers) and entries curated from
punkpeye/awesome-mcp-servers; those run as separate processes via npx/uvx and
are not redistributed here.
